        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-5581" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-5581" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>&#8222;It&#8217;s only<br />
after we&#8217;ve lost everything, that we are free to do anything.&#8221;<br />
&#8222;Stop being<br />
afraid. Accept (not pretend to accept and fear) that pain and death are a part<br />
of life. So is failure,﻿<br />
embarrassment etc. So don&#8217;t let it hold you back. Stop hiding behind religion,<br />
social clicks, drugs, video games whatever it is that makes you feel safe is<br />
holding you back!&#8221;</p>
